					<p class="paragrafoPost">
						ERP means Enterprise Resource Planning. It`s an information 
						system that manages all the operations of your enterprise. 
						It takes care from the payment of the employees, to the revenues, 
						including the business process management. Thus, all the 
						administration and operation related of the enterprise 
						that can be done digitally is done in the ERP.
					</p>
